'Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊潰了前來的木葉增援部隊
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出壓倒性力量的佩因
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策的木葉忍者們
'Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人為了村子
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人為了保護重要的人
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在絕境之中
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所能做出的最佳選擇是
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
'Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因VS卡卡西

Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉發動襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說曉來襲 當真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來襲擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是擊敗了自來也的曉的首領 佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他不但殺害了自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後還親自出馬襲擊木葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為了收集尾獸四處狩獵人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括砂隱的一尾在內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計大半的人柱力都已落入他們之手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們此行的目的到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代火影的遺產 漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是面對這場危機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五代居然想把鳴人召回村子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣豈不是火上澆油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再繼續任由第五代胡來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉會就此滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉潛入了村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅老師 麻煩你退後一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 快從地下通道前往避難所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在途中保護您的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師和腹中的胎兒有任何閃失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都無顏面對阿斯瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真看不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經能同自然一體化到如此地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這個修行可以告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 深作大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 深作大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小自來也果然沒有看走眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子能夠超越小自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快從我身上挪開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人這個大白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把藥丸都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就麻煩你做臨場指揮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還在驗屍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷員實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫療忍者們都亂了分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有人在現場指揮的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我擔負這麼多人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 如果是綱手大人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃一個加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給傷員們服用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠行走的人請自行前往避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不久之後將會送來更多的傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要立刻接受救治的重傷者標為紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠延遲救治的標為黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅是輕傷 請繫上綠色緞帶進行區分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也該回去了 這裡就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 能呼吸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去叫鳴人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鳴人留在妙木山好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽說襲擊木葉的正是曉的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還瞄準了鳴人這個人柱力不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者不是連自來也都擊敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鳴人被打敗  九尾落入他們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再管我了 鳴人 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死了 夢想什麼的也都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 躲開 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在成為火影之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人的仇由我來報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能靜靜的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但靜心一想 就發覺並不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的使命是成為下一代的榜樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並幫助他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我隨時都能笑著賭上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白那孩子是多麼仰慕小自來也了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的希望他就是那個預言之子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小自來也已經將一切都托付給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…不打算放手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算對身為顧問的我們做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問你們打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把他當成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的意志已經被繼承並且培養出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在正要超越自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他並非是木葉用來抑制戰爭的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是守護木葉的一個忍者 漩渦鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也 還有猿飛老師 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及砂隱的千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有而你們卻欠缺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要教你們我所寫的辭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對記不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫小傢伙說的也是實情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也不勉強你們全部記住並理解其中的意味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 希望你們長大之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能記得我這個老頭曾經說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你們的將來一定會起到作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「火之意志」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有樹葉飛舞的地方 火就會燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火的影子會照耀著村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並讓新的樹葉發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個由我們這些無聊的老人創造的忍者世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能出現像你這樣的人我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的我做盡了錯事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後總算做了件正確的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱和木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此後的未來一定會有別於我們的時代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西所說的 你那股不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量應該會大大改變未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為一位前所未見的火影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿飛老師 以及砂隱的千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們擁有 而你們卻不具備的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…相信的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同我的祖父初代火影相信你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把木葉托付給你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你們相信孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把希望托付給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西像是接收查克拉信號的接收器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈滿了佩因的全身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據深作大人描述
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六個佩因的身體和臉部全都佈滿了這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 這六個人全身都能接收某種查克拉信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後借此行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未瞭解得如此透徹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是接收器…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用於查克拉相互通信的無線電呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西目前正在反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該跟佩因強大的秘密有關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會配合審問班的情報來解開謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情報部的報告 敵人正在搜尋鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以入侵村子的敵人肯定是佩因沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來最好將所有情況都呈報給深作大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召回鳴人的時候順便轉達此事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音 帶上驗屍情報和審問班碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查明佩因是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗部「燈」班保護靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便擔任審問班的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓那些傢伙接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在屋頂等待情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便通過蛞蝓治療所有傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力守住村子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得趕快去找深作大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白活了這麼多年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被綱手鎮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能困住九尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 漩渦鳴人在不在這個村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 能把術吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻跟在木葉所有的忍者以及村民身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後通過我的查克拉治療所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來村子正面臨危機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 都要守住這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上火影之名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出九尾人柱力的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個紋樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…這傢伙就是曉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你這種傢伙我無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒你什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大肆製造騷亂吸引注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後暗中搜索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上傷者趕快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就問你吧 九尾在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的都是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人和其他村子不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算會丟掉自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有人會出賣自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出壓倒性力量的佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策的木葉忍者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在絕境之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所能做出的最佳選擇是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:22:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因VS卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人迷惑的過去世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一起戰鬥嗎 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一彈劇場版預售券的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是限定版文件夾哦
